  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is-- this is what should I say, what should [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I eat? ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So this is the story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I kept plenty-- plenty of times of my mind-- my sister with the kids, the parents, the other sister, the other sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other sister was in Plaszow, you know, [INAUDIBLE] Krakow, the one who brought me food, a package.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was still in Krakow and her husband was coming-- he was in Tarnov.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] he came home to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she was also living with us, but then when she had the baby, she-- she had to go to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So what do I want to say?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was thinking about the family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Plenty of times I was thinking about the family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- she-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] her husband to get her to-- to-- they-- they evacuated all Krakow, the ghetto, at that time, and they sended-- sent the young people to Plaszow, whatever, to the camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Now that [INAUDIBLE] I forget, I black out, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And with-- and with her husband's mother was also the there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mother and she with the baby and her sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the Polack went out and brought them-- and he left them outside by a Polack and he went into the camp to make connections to go to Hungary, which he did.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Hungary-- but-- from Hungary to Romania, he did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But before he did, he had in mind to bring the family, too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the Polack went out and brought in the Germans and they-- and they made-- they-- they made-- they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the way, I have the pictures to here when I was in Poland and I was [INAUDIBLE], which-- which he he brought her out after the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
